Class AbstractDiagnosisCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mmm.cms.homehealth.AbstractDiagnosisCode

    public abstract class AbstractDiagnosisCode
extends java.lang.Object
implements DiagnosisCodeIF, java.lang.Cloneable
    Provides the base information about a Diagnosis or Procedure code, including the code value, type, and associated Group.

    3M HIS
